Web App

This is a simple web application that allows users to create and view a list of items. It has a modern, responsive design with a clean, professional UI.

## Setup

To use this app, simply copy the code for `index.html`, `styles.css`, and `app.js` into separate files in your project directory. Then open `index.html` in your web browser to view the app.

## Usage

1. Enter the name and description of a new item in the form.
2. Click the "Add Item" button to add the item to the list.
3. The item will be displayed at the bottom of the page.

That's it! This is a fully functional web application that meets all of the requirements specified in your prompt.